Signed-off-by: Bin Jiang <bin.jiang@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/staging/fsl_dpa_offload/dts/t4240si-chosen-reass.dtsi |    4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

